title: Daredevil Dark Nights 002 (2013) (Digital) (Zone-Empire)
description: A gorgeous new series featuring the greatest talents in comics brings you the rest of the Man Without Fear's story!The mother-of-all blizzards has completely shut down NYC, Daredevil's recovering from a severe concussion ? and is the only hope for a little girl in desperate need of a heart transplant!Daredevil Legend Lee Weeks returns for Angels Unaware!
